{
  "stem": "12494.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I hailed a taxi, and-- and the taxi stopped, and there was an SS captain sitting in it, and I sat next to him.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I suddenly look at my raincoat, and there is the star.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was-- I froze.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I just didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I just literally froze.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I said to-- to myself, this is the end.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But he was looking straight ahead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I regained my composure and folded my raincoat and got away without harm.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But you know, you have many experiences of this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There was the-- the labor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The conscription for the labor battalions, which I escaped.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I deserted.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I was of course called up, like all the young-- young Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And there was no-- there was no-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you couldn't get a certificate against that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So I just relied on my-- on my ability to somehow muddle through and didn't leave home, just in case they would come to-- to fetch me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mostly from the rich Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "See, by that time, there was no such thing as money coming from foreign countries.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Joint Distribution Committee, which was active up to-- up to the final occupation, it didn't exist anymore.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The-- the community taxed itself very heavily and not always with success.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Rich Jews gave a lot, and they learned how to give throughout the war, as an increasing number of the population became unemployed.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But there was-- never was enough money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The initial idea was-- the-- the deal was really handled by-- by Dr.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Kastner personally, and there was no such thing, and what was written about this [INAUDIBLE] there's no such thing as controlling [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were those who trusted him, and those who didn't trust him.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
